    "text": "FAMILY IS BEING SCRUTINIZED AS"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499332,
    "endTime": 502568,
    "duration": 3236,
    "text": "MUCH ANYMORE, ALTHOUGH THIS GUY"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501701,
    "endTime": 503636,
