    "duration": 3504,
    "text": "THAT WAS MAYBE A GOOD THING."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 558024,
    "endTime": 562595,
    "duration": 4571,
    "text": "THROUGH THE LAST NINE DAYS SINCE"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 559959,
    "endTime": 564297,
    "duration": 4338,
    "text": "WE BECAME AWARE OF IT, IT SEEMS"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562695,
